Target 1 "Junk Warrior" you control; this turn, if it battles an opponent's monster, apply these effects.● Your opponent cannot activate cards or effects until the end of the Damage Step.● If it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent.● Double any battle damage your opponent takes from battles involving it.● It cannot be destroyed by battle.● Destroy that opponent's monster at the end of the Damage Step.
